{"tid":139264,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"廢青日記, 今日終於見識到啲家長點樣戇鳩","createTime":"2017-03-01T09:32:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T16:54:50.000Z","uid":47356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de1e97175eb2f7b28b37856c4df23a7a20a1df52","tid":139264,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T09:32:57.000Z","msg":"小弟只係一個廢青, 話說有日去學結他, <br />\n準備走既時候有個家長走左入黎, 見到啊sir就開始講,<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 家長 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Sir<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 啊sir, 你可唔可以逼下我個女落左堂之後都要練結他呀,<br />\n我見佢番左屋企都係hea既, 都唔係練既<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : ..... (無奈中)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 同埋想睇下有無邊日可以加多15分鐘或者一星期上多堂呀<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 其實啊女一直都學得幾好喎...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 但係佢番到去唔練呢, (重點黎) 呀女仲話想買枝結他, 不過心諗佢都練唔好買左咪又係哂錢<br />\n------------------------然後我已經走左--------------------------<br />\n<br />\n連結他都無都算, 全程既對話其實個女, 姐係個學生, 都企左係到, <br />\n自己唔識教女走上黎嘈都算,仲好意思要求加鐘, 平日已經藝術家脾氣既啊sir面都黑埋, 結局當然無睇到啦, 不過陣係想講啲家長真係好鬼野蠻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁既人就真係不如唔好生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da9cf9a218ab0e9ee0225cf42ed6199298c439c2","tid":139264,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T09:34:07.000Z","msg":"仲有學咩都係,唔會係一朝一夕就識囉, 咁既心態學乜都係多餘, 收得你千幾蚊仲埋你啊媽好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6456049c24613609cfc9b0ea2b0e4ab79bf1f2","tid":139264,"uid":16096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T09:36:36.000Z","msg":"我見佢番左屋企都係hea既, 都唔係練既<br />\n<br />\n但係屋企無結他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd192c18d1e4a51745e2847c37885626015b15e","tid":139264,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T09:36:44.000Z","msg":"阿女無結他，咁返到屋企係練乜？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申︰未學過結他"},{"pid":"a27b450cef5c29784e7c0a5520b9fa9bdf5f8a0e","tid":139264,"uid":37463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T09:37:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>阿女無結他，咁返到屋企係練乜？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申︰未學過結他</blockquote><br />\n我都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"144062c571606557844e517d94d01e0fcb22dd44","tid":139264,"uid":40499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T09:42:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我見佢番左屋企都係hea既, 都唔係練既<br />\n<br />\n但係屋企無結他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拎個掃把練住先"},{"pid":"17d378e70f11798f32b43b4115305a3395b48a32","tid":139264,"uid":38253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T09:44:04.000Z","msg":"&quot;阿SIR呀,大約學幾耐先彈到一首歌呀?&quot;"},{"pid":"5a4841a8858e9e9b1e77ab9374eb117e51121ea3","tid":139264,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T09:44:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>阿女無結他，咁返到屋企係練乜？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申︰未學過結他</blockquote><br />\n佢老豆睇謝霆鋒大？"},{"pid":"8b012a59748292e86b7c716b29f10350ea8cfaa5","tid":139264,"uid":14716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T09:44:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我見佢番左屋企都係hea既, 都唔係練既<br />\n<br />\n但係屋企無結他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拎個掃把練住先</blockquote><br />\n我平時屋企都係咁<br />\n<br />\n練到彈到hotel California solo<br />\n<br />\n跟住無玩"},{"pid":"19a1543b8335f1aa4f2595bb68a8b86e6f935323","tid":139264,"uid":60297,"like":0,"disli